name: This Is Still Not A Design ⎨DML1306⎬
description:
While beginning a new semester, just wanted students to express themselves =)
This is by a group of students who’d been attending classes online for 2 years.

Here’s one from a series of art-jam when asked “Where do you wish to travel?”

I promised to mint on their behalf. Hope it gives them some idea about NFTs.
!!!100% sales will contribute directly to their class funds!!!
